    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions as <i>mirror hideaway</i>, except any creature that enters the target mirror can spend a swift action to exit through another mirror within 500 feet as if using <i>dimension door</i>; this is a one-way transport. The creature can exit through a mirror only if it could fit through an opening the same size as the mirror. Each transport through the target mirror reduces the spell's duration by 1 hour.</p>"
